From joseph dale fisher Subject Re Deification In article A HOLFELTZ writes Aaron Bryce Cardenas writes After all what does prophesy mean Secondly what is an Apostle Answer an especial witness one who is suppose to be a personal That means to be a true apostle one must have Christ appear to Now lets see when did the church quit claiming Actually an apostle is someone who is If you will mailmen could be called apostles in that However with Jesus they were designated and were given Remember that there were many thousands of people who witnessed what Jesus That didn't make them apostles Joe Fisher